test_even_n_range:
assert [64, 66] == [130, 132, 134]
  At index 0 diff: 64 != 130
  Right contains one more item: 134
  Full diff:
  - [130, 132, 134]
  + [64, 66]
test_all_negative_one_range:
assert [64, 66] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 64
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [64, 66]
test_negative_odd_range:
assert [64, 66] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 64
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [64, 66]
